{"tid":1395313,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(突發)女子地鐵上撒尿倒昆蟲 列車被迫停止運行","createTime":"2019-08-01T16:59:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T17:40:55.000Z","uid":37053,"like":2,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b28cc7b673b4dcdeb0c9c4d5d2bbedbc017904de","tid":1395313,"uid":37053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:59:01.000Z","msg":"近日，紐約地鐵上發生了可怕的一幕，一名瘋狂的女子把一桶<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">活蹦亂跳的昆蟲全都倒在了車廂里</span></span></strong>，並在眾目睽睽之下撒尿，這一系列行為讓所有乘客都陷入了恐慌。<br />\n事情發生在8月24日下午6點，車廂里擠滿了下班的乘客。據目擊者描述，當時肇事女子遭到了一群年輕人的推擠，還被打了臉。緊接着，意想不到的一幕發生了。該女子拿出了裝有<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>蟋蟀和蠕蟲</strong></span>的桶，開始把這些昆蟲撒向空中。受到驚嚇的乘客們大聲喊叫着跑向車廂的一端。<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>有人按下了緊急制動裝置</strong></span>，列車在曼哈頓橋上停了15分鐘。更糟糕的是，車內的空調也停止了工作。驚恐的乘客被困在悶熱的車廂里，手臂上爬滿蟋蟀，有人甚至開始嘔吐。然而此時該女子竟然開始在地板上撒尿，把躲避昆蟲的乘客又趕向了車廂的另一端。<br />\n<br />\n混亂中，幾名男子試圖按住發瘋的女子，但該女子卻開始向他們吐唾沫。乘客拍攝的視頻顯示，該女子一邊用頭撞擊車廂門，一邊大喊，「你們為什麼要撞我?全車的人都是因為你們晚點的。」<br />\n20分鐘後，列車再次啟動，並於下午6點30分到達迪卡爾布大道站。警察隨即帶走了這名女子。目前，該女子已被送往醫院的精神科進行觀察。幸運的是，並沒有乘客在混亂中受傷。（中國青年網編譯報道）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/xKa3Sa9Y6Fs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FxKa3Sa9Y6Fs&d=oOhF4K9gmG%2F73F8T9h6VFPzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=6e8f21de\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/xKa3Sa9Y6Fs</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/CkPyitNVI78\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FCkPyitNVI78&d=oOhF4K9gmG%2F73F8T9h6VFPzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=457bb592\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/CkPyitNVI78</a> <br />\n<br />\n好彩港鐵一向乾淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果地鐵有木蝨我真係唔知點番工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23896e7fa064c68a790b287d792687d1d8052e27","tid":1395313,"uid":37053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:59:42.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"d7eab4d5e6bf414551c3201d0e6b6f6710564a3b","tid":1395313,"uid":37053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:59:54.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"2bf75baec808b1f227f249c35beadad6e494110e","tid":1395313,"uid":37053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T17:00:04.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"4c3d1e2465744f09552014055857f95a86d0ac1d","tid":1395313,"uid":37053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T17:00:14.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"3a579fdd54f61dbc39628b49ac05ae52b1eac233","tid":1395313,"uid":37053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T17:00:24.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"e017b989577bd572bdf69153d7f4dd66e5f52e3d","tid":1395313,"uid":37053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T17:00:35.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"baebed074ab2b823918e8b63b1d410eab3dab5ea","tid":1395313,"uid":37053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T17:00:45.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"6fff7378eda6f1a493269463888f1b656024e818","tid":1395313,"uid":37053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T17:00:56.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"87fbd5207ae0cd91b4a6917d92d3a67e0f9493ab","tid":1395313,"uid":9315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T17:01:02.000Z","msg":"係狗署搞咪算  狗有蝨係正常不過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3d3f53f45a4516547c831e34348cb3cb75e5d7f","tid":1395313,"uid":37053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T17:01:06.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"908b9b1c212b14b4740346f1c8bc0e94df8b9f1e","tid":1395313,"uid":37053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T17:01:17.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"f97b2ab543d1bd990d42b6381e48e8f9c4aadb66","tid":1395313,"uid":269763,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T17:02:00.000